BRIGGS et al., Appellants, v. CLARK, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. December 8, 1893.) Action by Leah V. Briggs and others against Azzle Clark.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, without costs. Action upon the appeal suspended.
